  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the impact of and response by physicians on Hospital&#xD;
      Medicine/General Internal Medicine service to a notification identifying seriously ill&#xD;
      patients at high risk of death within 30 days as well as within 6 months in a cluster&#xD;
      randomized control trial.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
